, (d)-(i)","option_c_hi":"(a)-(iii), (b)-(iv), (c)-(i), (d)-(ii)","option_d_hi":"(a)-(ii), (b)-(i), (c)-(iv), (d)-(iii)"},{"id":73,"quiz_id":7,"topic_id":1002,"sort_order":3,"question":"Consider the following statements regarding Rakhigarhi:\\n\\n1. It is the largest Indus Valley Civilization site located in India.\\n\\n2. It is located in the Hisar district of Haryana on the Ghaggar-Hakra river plain.\\n\\n3. The site was extensively excavated by Amarendra Nath of the Archaeological Survey of India.\\n\\nWhich of the statements given above are correct?","question_hi":"राखीगढ़ी के संबंध में निम्नलिखित कथनों पर विचार करें:\\n\\n1. यह भारत में स्थित सबसे बड़ा सिंधु घाटी सभ्यता स्थल है।\\n\\n2. यह घग्गर-हकरा नदी के मैदान पर हरियाणा के हिसार जिले में स्थित है।\\n\\n3. भारतीय पुरातत्व सर्वेक्षण के अमरेंद्र नाथ द्वारा इस स्थल का व्यापक रूप से उत्खनन किया गया था।\\n\\nऊपर दिए गए कथनों में से कौन से सही हैं?","option_a":"1 and 2 only","option_b":"2 and 3 only","option_c":"1 and 3 only","option_d":"1, 2 and 3","option_a_hi":"केवल 1 और 2","option_b_hi":"केवल 2 और 3","option_c_hi":"केवल 1 और 3","option_d_hi":"1, 2 और 3"},{"id":74,"quiz_id":7,"topic_id":1002,"sort_order":4,"question":"Which of the following sites uniquely yielded evidence of an inkpot, a footprint of a dog chasing a cat, and a major bead-making factory?","question_hi":"निम्नलिखित में से किस स्थल से विशिष्ट रूप से एक दवात (inkpot), एक कुत्ते द्वारा बिल्ली का पीछा करने के पदचिह्न और एक प्रमुख मनका बनाने के कारखाने के साक्ष्य मिले हैं?","option_a":"Chanhudaro","option_b":"Banawali","option_c":"Kalibangan","option_d":"Sutkagen Dor","option_a_hi":"चन्हुदड़ो","option_b_hi":"बनावली","option_c_hi":"कालीबंगन","option_d_hi":"सुत्कागेंडोर"},{"id":75,"quiz_id":7,"topic_id":1002,"sort_order":5,"question":"Assertion (A): In Kalibangan, both the citadel and the lower town were separately fortified with mud-brick walls.\\n\\nReason (R): Kalibangan served as the supreme imperial capital of the entire Indus Valley Civilization.\